articles.title: [Watch] Trent Boult Traps Reeza Hendricks For Golden Duck In World Cup Return - OneCricket
articles.description: Trent Boult returned to the World Cup in a spectacular manner, pinning Reeza Hendricks for leg-before on Monday during New Zealand’s warm-up fixture against South Africa, taking place in Thiruvananthapuram.
